text: Stein Holsvik (born 13 October 1969) is a retired Norwegian football striker. Hailing from Volda, he started his senior career in Volda TI. Ahead of the 1991 season he joined the regional first-tier club Molde FK. After one season and 2 goals in 5 first-tier games, he returned to Volda. He played for Hødd from 1994 through 1998, getting another first-tier season in 1995.
